### **2. Missing Error Boundaries**
❌ No error handling UI components

**Add:**
- [app/error.tsx](app/error.tsx) (route-level errors)
- [app/global-error.tsx](app/global-error.tsx) (global errors)
- Custom ErrorBoundary component for granular error handling

---

### **3. Poor State Management Pattern**
⚠️ **Token stored in BOTH localStorage AND Zustand store**

**Issues:**
- Duplication in [api-client.ts](api-client.ts#L106) and [authStore.ts](authStore.ts#L37)
- Security risk (localStorage accessible via XSS)

**Fix:**
- Use **httpOnly cookies** for tokens (most secure)
- Or consolidate to Zustand only
- Remove direct localStorage access

---

### **4. Missing Provider Service Integration**
❌ As per previous report:
- No provider list page
- No provider detail page  
- No service catalog display
- Frontend service methods defined but unused

---

### **5. No Loading States & Skeletons**
⚠️ Only basic `<Loading />` spinner

**Add:**
- Skeleton loaders for better UX
- Suspense boundaries with fallbacks
- Optimistic UI updates

